title: `$set::post()`
description: Set value to `$_POST` array.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
Set::post($key = null, $value = null);
Set::post($value = []);
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
Set::post('user', '@ta-tau-taufik');
~~~

~~~ .php
Set::post([
    'user' => '@ta-tau-taufik',
    'pass' => 'b4d455'
]);
~~~